u are going to GFay as I'm porting there after this and you will have to wait.&quot;<br><br>idiot_raider03: &quot;Can you TL me out in a minute or 2?&quot;<br>idiot_raider04: &quot;Can you TL me to GFay?&quot;<br><br>/em shoots himself in the head<br><br>What the hell is wrong with these people?!? I guess it's because on my server, Vox and Nagafen are mostly pick-up raids instead of a guild raid or even a group of friends.<br><br>I hit 53 a few days ago so I can't even do these raids anymore but reading the chat pet peeves post on the main board reminded me of all this. <p><center><p><hr WIDTH="100%"><br><img SRC="http://home.pacbell.net/mark3264/thor_and_alts.jpg" height=178 width=658></center><center><table BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 ><tr><td><table WIDTH="111" ><tr><td NOWRAP style="filter:glow(color=#FF0000" strength="1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt'"><center><font face="Verdana,"><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=-1><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=253097" target="_blank">Baron ThorodelRedstorms</a></font></font></font><br><font face="Verdana,"><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=-1>Level 53Wizard</font></font></font></center></td></tr></table></td><td ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=CENTER WIDTH="52%"><table WIDTH="111" ><tr><td NOWRAP style="filter:glow(color=#FF0000" strength="1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt'"><center><font face="Verdana,"><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=-1><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=254166" target="_blank">Xanedhir</a></font></font></font><br><font face="Verdana,"><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=-1>Level 25Magician</font></font></font></center></td></tr></table></td><td><table WIDTH="111" ><tr><td NOWRAP style="filter:glow(color=#FF0000" strength="1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt'"><center><font face="Verdana,"><font color="#FFFFFF"><font size=-1><a hr