ve a problem with them again.<br><br>Sometimes, you just have to be an asshole to get things done. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwhizbangdustyboots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Gnomus Originalus</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/25/02 7:19:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1234.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/whiz-side-01.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gating people out after Vox/Nagafen raids</span><hr size=1> Better system:<br><br>&quot;No, motherfucker, I will not translocate you out of a raid zone. Those left behind are more vulnerable for your absence. I won't go on a two hour CR because you failed to do your homework and your mom is pissed now and we then eat a repop because your speedbump ass wasn't here to taunt. Since the raid is ending, we're going to all port to WC and deal with rollables there. Afterwards, you can camp your ass there, or I can translocate you then. Have a nice day.&quot;<br><br>Unless it's an emergency, no, you don't get a translocate out of a raid zone. Period. <p><a href="http://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=49189" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/whiz-photo-short.gif" height=60 width=468 alt="Whizbang Dustyboots" border=0></a><br><font size=1></font><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=41790" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/bottom.gif" height=12 width=239 alt="an enthralled  says 'Uoy ekil semong etah yllaeri!'" border=0 vspace=5></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaurianne.showPublicPro